<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: inherit;


        }

        html {
            font-size: 62.5%;
            line-height: 1.6rem;
            font-family: "Roboto", sans-serif;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            background-color: #e2e0e0;
            color: #261044;
            line-height: 1.3;
        }

        .navbar {
            color: #000000;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 14px;
            padding-bottom: 5px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            height: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #18ccfc, #6aba48);
            border-top-left-radius: 10px;
            border-top-right-radius: 10px;
            color: #fff;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .container {
            margin: auto auto;
            width: 550px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            z-index: 999;
            background-color: #fff;
        }

        .header {
            height: 280px;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: space-around;
        }

        .header .text {
            margin-top: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .message-welcome {
            padding: 0px 16px;
            font-size: 1.6rem;
        }

        .verify-code {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            padding-right: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            margin: auto;
            width: 150px;
            height: 40px;
            background-color: aquamarine;
            border-radius: 30px;
        }

        .verify-code p {
            margin-left: 20px;
            padding-top: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .footer-page {
            text-align: center;
            height: 150px;
            margin: 100px auto 0 auto;
            padding-top: 70px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #18ccfc, #6aba48);
            border-bottom-left-radius: 10px;
            border-bottom-right-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #fff;
            font-weight: 900;
        }

        .footer-page-background {
            height: 80%;
        }

        .seperate {
            margin-top: 50px;
            width: 100%;
            height: 3px;
            background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, #18ccfc, #6aba48);
        }

        .img-ava {
            margin-top: 13px;
            width: 80px;
        }

        .avatar {
            position: relative;
            top: 1250px;
            margin-left: 230px;
            position: absolute;
            background-color: #fff;
            width: 100px;
            height: 100px;
            border-radius: 100px;
        }

        .instruction__steps {
            list-style: none;
        }

        .instruction__steps-step img {
            width: 150px;
            border: 4px solid #371765;
            border-radius: 20px;
            margin-right: 16px;
            align-items: center;
        }

        .instruction__message {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;

        }

        .instruction__steps-step {
            display: flex;
            margin: 10px 16px 20px 16px;
        }

        .instruction__steps-step-text p:nth-child(1) {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #154d4b;
        }

        .instruction__steps-step-text p:nth-child(2) {
            font-size: 1.5rem;

        }

        .icons {
            margin: 16px 0px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .icons img {
            width: 32px;
            margin: 4px;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-bottom: 200px;
        }

        .footer p {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 2rem;
            font-weight: 800;
        }

        .download {
            margin: auto;
            width: 100px;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-around;

        }

        .download img {
            width: 165px;
            margin: 12px 30px;
        }

        .link {
            margin: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 1.4rem;
        }
    </style>
    <title>Document</title>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <nav class="navbar">Share and care</nav>

        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="./images/logo copy.png" alt="" />
            </div>
            <p class="text">Welcome to Share And Care, Khoa
                <p />
        </div>
        <div class="message-welcome">
            <p>
                Thank you for joining our mission to combat waste - we're grateful to
                have you on board
            </p>
            <p>
                How do I get involved? Our free app lets you share unwanted household
                items and surplus food with your local community - saving them from
                gathering dust on shelves, or being thrown in the bin.
            </p>
            <p>The verification code you need to access your account is:</p>
        </div>
        <div class="verify-code">
            <p>{{otpCode}}</p>
        </div>
        <div class="message-welcome">
            <p>The verification code will expire in 10 minutes</p>
            <p>
                If you don't request this code, someone may be trying to access your
                account.<strong>Do not forward or give this code to anyone</strong>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="seperate"></div>
        <div class="instruction">
            <p class="instruction__message">Share in just 3 simple steps
                <p />
            <ul class="instruction__steps">
                <li class="instruction__steps-step">
                    <img src="./images/itemImg.png" alt="">
                    <div class="instruction__steps-step-text">
                        <p>1. Pick your item</p>
                        <p>Gather up anything you no longer need, whether it's clothing, kids toys or food- you can add
                            almost anything.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="instruction__steps-step">
                    <img src="./images/addItem.png" alt="">
                    <div class="instruction__steps-step-text">
                        <p>2. Add your items</p>
                        <p>Share your items to Olio by tapping the green "+" button at the bottom of the screen. Just
                            click "free" and the type of item you'd like to share.</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
                <li class="instruction__steps-step">
                    <img src="./images/confirm.png" alt="">
                    <div class="instruction__steps-step-text">
                        <p>3. Confirm details</p>
                        <p>Then fill in some details! Add pictures, a description to gain interest, as well as how and
                            when you'd like to share. Voil√†!</p>
                    </div>
                </li>
            </ul>
        </div>

        <div class="footer-page">
            <div class="avatar"><img class="img-ava" src="./images/Rectangle 1093.png" alt=""></div>
            <p>some one in here</p>
        </div>

    </div>
    <footer class="footer">
        <div class="icons">
            <img src="./images/icon_fb.png" alt="">
            <img src="./images/icon_ig.png" alt="">
            <img src="./images/icon_tw.png" alt="">
            <img src="./images/icon_tt.png" alt="">
        </div>
        <p>Get Share And Care App</p>
        <div class="download">
            <div class="ggplay">
                <img src="./images/PlayStore.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="appstore">
                <img src="./images/AppStore.png" alt="">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="link">
            <span>1 Vo Van Ngan, Linh Chieu Ward, Thu Duc City, Ho Chi Minh City.<span />
        </div>

    </footer>
</body>

</html>